_sText:
Surf_lepidus, a staged skillsurf map with 7 stages, one bonus and no jail. The entrance to the bonus stage is on stage 5, first to complete it gets a knife. Not much to say really, other than that I have tried my best to come up with original ways to make this a challenging and enjoyable map.

Requirements: sv_airaccelerate 150, a tickrate of 66 and noblock.
